<em>Published in final edited form as: </em>J Biomed Inform. 2017 Oct 24;76:9–18. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jbi.2017.10.008" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1016/j.jbi.2017.10.008</a>
</div>
